  "llmDescription": "Local LTX 2.3 image-to-video using kijai/ComfyUI-PromptRelay with a fixed 4-segment timeline. Each segment is anchored by an image guide and a per-segment prompt, with a single global prompt patched across the model. Designed for longer multi-shot sequences in a single render.",
